    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/text/git/raw/master/adguard.png" alt="AdGuard"></p><p>   AdGuard规则,AdGuard</p><h2 id="Write-By-Hacamer"><a href="#Write-By-Hacamer" class="headerlink" title="Write By Hacamer"></a>Write By Hacamer</h2><h3 id="更新时间：2021年6月4日08-23-27"><a href="#更新时间：2021年6月4日08-23-27" class="headerlink" title="更新时间：2021年6月4日08:23:27"></a>更新时间：2021年6月4日08:23:27</h3><h3 id="自定义过滤器"><a href="#自定义过滤器" class="headerlink" title="自定义过滤器"></a>自定义过滤器</h3><p>adgk：<a href="https://banbendalao.coding.net/p/adgk/d/ADgk/git/raw/master/ADgk.txt">https://banbendalao.coding.net/p/adgk/d/ADgk/git/raw/master/ADgk.txt</a></p><p>My AdFilters(for PC）：<a href="https://halflife.coding.net/p/list/d/list/git/raw/master/ad-pc.txt">https://halflife.coding.net/p/list/d/list/git/raw/master/ad-pc.txt</a></p><h3 id="DNS过滤器"><a href="#DNS过滤器" class="headerlink" title="DNS过滤器"></a>DNS过滤器</h3><p>anti_ad:<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/anti-AD/git/raw/master/anti-ad-adguard.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/anti-AD/git/raw/master/anti-ad-adguard.txt</a></p><p>AdGuard DNS过滤器：<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror/git/raw/master/AdGuard-Simplified-Domain-Names-Filter.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror/git/raw/master/AdGuard-Simplified-Domain-Names-Filter.txt</a></p><p>Adaway: <a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adaway.rule/git/raw/master/hosts.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adaway.rule/git/raw/master/hosts.txt</a></p><p>Hacamer的DNS规则：<a href="https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/some-rule(dns).txt">https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/some-rule(dns).txt</a></p><p>白名单<br>冷漠维护的白名单：<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Potterli20/filtering@master/filtering.txt">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Potterli20/filtering@master/filtering.txt</a></p><h3 id="Hacamer的规则"><a href="#Hacamer的规则" class="headerlink" title="Hacamer的规则"></a>Hacamer的规则</h3><p>自己随便写的规则(去哔哩哔哩网页打开app提示)：<br><a href="https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/not-app.txt">https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/not-app.txt</a></p><p>自己搜集的用户规则(From CoolApk)：<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/adgurd/d/adrules/git/raw/master/rules-admin.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/adgurd/d/adrules/git/raw/master/rules-admin.txt</a></p><p>自己搜集的DNS规则(From CoolApk)：<br><a href="https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/some-rule(dns).txt">https://gitee.com/hacamer/some-web-advertising-rules/raw/master/some-rule(dns).txt</a></p><p>合并规则(不建议使用）：<br>ALL:<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-all.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-all.txt</a><br>ALL-lengmo:<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-lengmo.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-lengmo.txt</a><br>ALL-xiaozhong:<br><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-xiaozhong.txt">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/lite/d/adsrules/git/raw/master/ALL-xiaozhong.txt</a></p><h3 id="国外规则-Cdn列表"><a href="#国外规则-Cdn列表" class="headerlink" title="国外规则-Cdn列表"></a>国外规则-Cdn列表</h3><p>广告规则cdn加速列表(链接是Github的镜像）：<br><a href="https://hub.fastgit.org/hacamer/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror">https://hub.fastgit.org/hacamer/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror</a></p><p><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/public/lite/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror/git/files">https://hacamer.coding.net/public/lite/AdBlock-Rules-Mirror/git/files</a></p><p> 注:My AdFilters (for PC)，adgk，neodev过滤效果过于强大，慎用！<br>以上规则必须开启https过滤（将证书移动到系统分区），否则过滤效果将下降！<br>这些规则AdGuardHome也可以用，但效果比AdGuard差一点,可以去试试<br>配置文件备份(微云)：</p><p><a href="https://share.weiyun.com/I7Fyjfs6">https://share.weiyun.com/I7Fyjfs6</a></p><p><a href="https://hacamer.coding.net/p/adgurd/d/adgp/git/raw/master/adg_2021_6_1.json?download=true">https://hacamer.coding.net/p/adgurd/d/adgp/git/raw/master/adg_2021_6_1.json?download=true</a></p><p>注:上面的配置文件配置的规则过滤效果非常强大，请酌情启用或禁用规则。另外，本人对小部分应用进行了白名单处理（即不拦截广告），请自行查看!</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
